&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;관련 글&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;a href=&quot;http://macnews.tistory.com/3371&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;구글, 용량 무제한 사진 저장 서비스 ‘구글 포토’ 출시&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;a href=&quot;http://macnews.tistory.com/2074&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;구글 드라이브 가격 인하… 100GB에 월 2달러 1TB에 월 10달러&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• &lt;a href=&quot;http://macnews.tistory.com/3036&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;맥용 '사진(Photos)'에 관해 알아두어야 할 스무가지&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/original/2764344E56BEBE6E31509E&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/image/2764344E56BEBE6E31509E&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/deed.ko&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;
